## 8. COMPLETE STRATEGY EXAMPLES

### 8.1 Beginner: Simple RSI

```
BACKTEST "Simple RSI"
MARKET NSE
TICKER RELIANCE
PERIOD 1Y

USE RSI(14)

BUY  WHEN RSI < 30
SELL WHEN RSI > 70

CAPITAL 500000
STOP_LOSS 5%
```

**Logic:** Buy when oversold, sell when overbought. 5% safety net.

---

### 8.2 Classic: MACD + RSI Filter

```
BACKTEST "RSI + MACD Crossover"
MARKET NSE
TICKER MARUTI
PERIOD 1Y

USE RSI(14)
USE MACD(12, 26, 9)

BUY  WHEN RSI > 30 AND MACD CROSSES_ABOVE SIGNAL
SELL WHEN RSI > 70 OR MACD CROSSES_BELOW SIGNAL

CAPITAL 100000
POSITION_SIZE 100%
STOP_LOSS 5%
TAKE_PROFIT 15%
COMMISSION 0.1%
```

**Logic:** Enter on MACD bullish cross (only if RSI confirms not overbought). Exit on RSI overbought OR MACD bearish cross.

---

### 8.3 Mean Reversion: Bollinger Bounce

```
BACKTEST "Bollinger Bounce"
MARKET NSE
TICKER HDFCBANK
PERIOD 6M

USE BB(20)
USE RSI(14)

BUY  WHEN CLOSE < BB_LOWER AND RSI < 35
SELL WHEN CLOSE > BB_MID OR RSI > 65

CAPITAL 300000
STOP_LOSS 3%
TAKE_PROFIT 8%
COMMISSION 0.1%
```

**Logic:** Buy when price falls below lower Bollinger Band with RSI confirmation. Sell at mid-band reversion. Conservative stops.

---

### 8.4 Trend Following: SMA + ADX

```
BACKTEST "SMA Trend + ADX Filter"
MARKET US
TICKER AAPL
PERIOD 2Y

USE SMA(50)
USE EMA(20)
USE ADX(14)
USE RSI(14)

BUY  WHEN CLOSE > SMA(50) AND EMA > SMA(50) AND ADX > 25 AND RSI > 40
SELL WHEN CLOSE < SMA(50) OR RSI > 80

CAPITAL 50000
POSITION_SIZE 100%
STOP_LOSS 7%
TAKE_PROFIT 20%
COMMISSION 0.05%
```

**Logic:** Buy only in strong uptrends (ADX > 25) when price and EMA are above SMA50. Wide stops for trend-following.

